                                    <h1 class="content__list__item__title--content"><span lang="fr">The history of <em>Citrus medica</em> (citron) in the Near East: Botanical remains and ancient art and texts</span></h1>
                                            <div class="content__list__item__authors content__list__item__authors--content">
                                    <a href="/pcjb/person/2185">Dafna Langgut</a>                            </div>
                                                                                                                                                                                    <div class="mb-3">
